description:
Cakes, Cupcakes, Cookies & Biscuits, Pastries, Brownies
I am a self-taught home baker that get very satisfied when I see people enjoying my bakes. Hence, I am on an adventure to let more people try out my food and collect feedback such that I can always improve and bring out better desserts to the table.Contact info is via DMs from insta, Facebook & Carousell.Delivery charges are charged based on locations and self pick up is at cashew MRT stationPreferred to pre-order 3 days in advance however if there are last min orders, it will then depends on time availability.
