Cakes, Birthday Cakes, Cupcakes, Cookies & Biscuits, Pies & Tarts, Pastries
Our launch menu consists of Tarte au Citron (Lemon Tart), Tiramisu, Uji Matcha Tiramisu, Butter Cookies with assorted flavours and Crunchy Chocolate Chip Cookies! Bestsellers would be our Tarte au Citron (Lemon Tart) and Earl Grey Butter Cookie!! Follow us on Instagram @MochaBakehouse/ WhatsApp us at +65 9712 5107 for queries/ to order! Islandwide delivery: $6. Self-Collection at S793472. We can also help you handwrite a short note if you decide to send the sweet treats as gifts!
