Cakes, Cookies & Biscuits, Pastries, Festive Baked Goods (Christmas), Brownies, Muffins (Chocolate, Vanilla, Banana, Citrus and Coffee)
I’m a home-baker who loves to share my bakes with those around me!Here are some of my specialities: fudgy cocoa-espresso brownies, chocolate-chunk cookies, mini basque-burnt cheesecake, lemon loaf (with homemade lemon curd) and apple crumble !!
You can contact me / order my bakes through dm on IG
@zoetbakeDelivery/Self pick-up daily from 3pm-8pm as I bake fresh daily!
