Cakes, Cupcakes, Cookies & Biscuits, Pies & Tarts, Festive Baked Goods (Chinese New Year, Christmas), Fondant Cake Toppers
We are a small and humble business and our goal is to put smiles on our customers' faces! Our chef has been trained in pastry and has a food hygiene certificate. Our specialties include our customised birthday cakes and tarts. Our popular items are earl grey buttercake and passionfruit tart! We do offer deliver and the option of self collection at Bukit batok/jurong east. Flavours of cake can be customized too!
