We’re a halal home based business and our most popular item would be our cinnamon rolls! Another favourite has to be our fudgy brownies, stuffed with Biscoff Cheesecake. We bake to order, & everything is baked fresh on day of delivery of self collection. To contact us, dm our instagram @bakingsoba, we offer island wide delivery (charged according to area), and self collection as well. To order, dm us :)
